OL,3,C'Putting manners' on the BBC: Gerry
OL,4,CAdams wins libel case
OL,6,FGerry Adams has said taking the BBC to
OL,7,Fcourt was about "putting manners" on
OL,8,Fthe broadcaster.
OL,10,FThe former leader of Sinn Fein has
OL,11,Fbeen awarded E100,000 (#84,000) in
OL,12,Fdamages after winning his libel action
OL,13,Fat the High Court in Dublin.
OL,15,FThe former Sinn Fein leader alleged a
OL,16,FBBC Spotlight programme, and an
OL,17,Faccompanying online story, defamed him
OL,18,Fby alleging he sanctioned the killing
OL,19,Fof former Sinn Fein official Denis
OL,20,FDonaldson. He denied any involvement.
