OL,6,FHe said: "I'm very mindful of the
OL,7,FDonaldson family in the course of this
OL,8,Flong trial, and indeed of the victims'
OL,9,Ffamilies who have had to watch all of
OL,10,Fthis.
OL,12,F"I want to say that the Justice
OL,13,FMinister Jim O'Callaghan should meet
OL,14,Fthe family of Denis Donaldson as
