OL,6,FBBC director Adam Smyth said there was
OL,7,Fdisappointment at the verdict.
OL,9,F"We believe we supplied extensive
OL,10,Fevidence to the court of the careful
OL,11,Feditorial process and journalistic
OL,12,Fdiligence applied to this programme
OL,13,Fand accompanying online article.
OL,15,F"Moreover, it was accepted by the
OL,16,Fcourt, and conceded by Gerry Adams'
OL,17,Flegal team, that the Spotlight
OL,18,Fbroadcast and publication were of the
OL,19,Fhighest public interest.
