OL,6,F"We didn't want to come to court, but
OL,7,Fit was important that we defend our
OL,8,Fjournalism and we stand by that
OL,9,Fdecision. Our past is difficult
OL,10,Fterrain for any jury and we thank them
OL,11,Ffor their diligence and careful
