OL,3,C'Putting manners' on the BBC: Gerry
OL,4,CAdams wins libel case
OL,6,F"The implications of their decision,
OL,7,Fthough, are profound. As our legal
OL,8,Fteam made clear, if the BBC's case
OL,9,Fcannot be won under existing Irish
OL,10,Fdefamation law, it's hard to see how
OL,11,Fanyone's could. And they warned that
OL,12,Ftoday's decision could hinder freedom
OL,13,Fof expression.
OL,15,F"Of course, a case of this importance,
OL,16,Fduration and complexity involves
OL,17,Fsignificant expense. In common with
OL,18,Fother media organisations the BBC has
OL,19,Finsurance and makes financial
OL,20,Fprovision for ongoing and anticipated
OL,21,Flegal claims.
