OL,6,F"We would like to thank Jennifer
OL,7,FO'Leary, Gwyneth Jones and all those
OL,8,Fwho gave evidence on behalf of the
OL,9,FBBC, as well as our legal team for
OL,10,Ftheir unwavering support. We will now
OL,11,Ftake some time with them to consider
OL,12,Fthe implications of this ruling."
OL,14,FSpotlight reporter Jennifer O'Leary
OL,15,Fthanked the legal team for their
OL,16,Fsupport.
OL,18,F"I said in the witness box that I had
OL,19,Fnothing to hide, only sources to
OL,20,Fprotect and I want to thank them for
OL,21,Ftrusting me," she added.
