OL,6,F"I also want to acknowledge and thank
OL,7,Four witnesses in court ` Trevor
OL,8,FRingland, Senator Michael McDowell and
OL,9,FAnn Travers ` who spoke so
OL,10,Fcourageously.
OL,12,F"And there are thousands of Ann
