OL,7,FDonegal in 2006, months after
OL,8,Fadmitting his role as a police and MI5
OL,9,Fagent over 20 years.
OL,11,FIn the programme broadcast in
OL,12,FSeptember 2016, an anonymous source
OL,13,Fgiven the pseudonym Martin claimed the
