OL,6,FThey were tasked with determining
OL,7,Fwhether the words in the BBC spotlight
OL,8,Fprogramme and accompanying article, on
OL,9,Fwhich Mr Adams brought the complaint,
OL,10,Fmean that he sanctioned and approved
OL,11,Fthe murder of Mr Donaldson.
OL,13,FMr Owens said they were to consider
OL,14,Fwhether it was "more likely than not"
OL,15,Fthat a "hypothetical reasonable
OL,16,Freader" would take that meaning from
OL,17,Fthe words.
